        <Parent_String>clinics (buildings, medical) [300006665], health facilities [300006653], health and welfare buildings [300006652], institutional buildings [300132384], single built works by function [300004894], single built works by specific type [300004795], single built works (built environment) [300004790], Single Built Works (hierarchy name) [300004789], Built Environment (hierarchy name) [300264550], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
